description.en: TIPINU token has been launched to act as the utility token for the NSFW 18+ streaming site cummuniti. The site is in development and is expected to rival the major adult content providers on it's debut with live streaming, chat, NFTs and more. TIPINU has 10 billion tokens on issue but only 250 million have been added to Pancake Swap. 97.5% of the supply is locked for major LP injection on cummuniti launch. Tokens that are not paired with the equivalent BNB will be burnt. Up to $10M of liquidity is to be raised to allow TIPINU to serve as payment currency for other adult content providers.
